\c 76 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 76\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Waaqayyo Mo'ichaan Beekamuu Isaa (Geggeessituu warra faarfatootaaf; faarfannaa Asaaf, isa mi'a ribuu qabuun faarfatamu; weedduu)
\m \bd 1\bd* Waaqayyo biyya Yihudaatti beekamaa dha, maqaan isaas biyya Israa'elitti guddaa dha.
\m \bd 2\bd* godoon isaa mandara Saalem keessa, iddoon buufata isaas Xiyoon keessa in dhaabate.
\m \bd 3\bd* Inni achitti xiyya phal phal jechaa adeemu, gaachana, billaa, mi'a lolaas in cabse.
\m \bd 4\bd* Ifni si irraa in finiina, tulloota "Tulluu boojuu" jedhamanii beekaman caalaattis ati surra-qabeessa.
\m \bd 5\bd* Warri onneen isaanii guutuu iyyuu mi'i isaanii saamamee, hirriba hin kaane in rafan; namoonni loltuun hundinuu, harka isaaniitiin waa hojjechuu hin dandeenye.
\m \bd 6\bd* Yaa Waaqayyo isa kan Yaaqoob! Ifata keetiin abbaan fardaa, fardi isaas of wallaalanii in ciciisu.\bd 7\bd* Ati garuu guddaa sodaachisaa dha, yeroo dheekkamsi kee ka'u, eenyu si dura dhaabachuu danda'a ree?
\m \bd 8\bd* Yeroo ati bantiiwwan waaqaa keessaa firdii dhageessifte, lafti immoo sodaattee calluma jette.
\m \bd 9\bd* Waaqayyo warra biyya lafaa kana irratti cunqurfaman oolchuudhaaf, firdii jabeessee dhaabuuf in ka'a.
\m \bd 10\bd* Dheekkamsi namootaa iyyuu ati caalaa akka jajamtu in godha, dheekkamsa isa irraa hafus akka mi'a miidhaginaatti ofitti in hidhatta.
\m \bd 11\bd* Wareega gooftaadhaaf wareegaa, isa wareegdanis Waaqayyo keessaniif baasaa! Warri naannoo isaa jiraatan hundinuu kennaa isaaf, isa sodaatamu sanaaf haa fidan!
\m \bd 12\bd* Inni hafuura isa warra gurguddoota keessaa ka'u gad in deebisa, inni mootota lafa irraas guddaa in sodaachisa.
\b 
